---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 font-sans selection:bg-purple-100 selection:text-purple-700">
		<Header />
		<main>
			<!-- Hero Section -->
			<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_-20%,#3b0764,#0f172a_80%)]"></div>
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-20 brightness-100 contrast-150"></div>
				
				<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
					<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
						<div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
							<div class="relative rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm leading-6 text-purple-300 ring-1 ring-purple-500/30 hover:ring-purple-500/50 transition-all bg-purple-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
								New Era of Coding with AI <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold ml-1">→</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-slate-400">
							Vibe Coding
						</h1>
						<p class="text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
							코드 너머의 흐름을 기록합니다. Astro와 AI가 만드는 새로운 개발 생태계 속에서 발견한 기술적 통찰과 노하우를 공유합니다.
						</p>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
							<a href="/blog" class="rounded-xl bg-purple-600 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20 hover:bg-purple-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-purple-400 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
								블로그 읽기
							</a>
							<a href="/about" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">
								About Me <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Decorative elements -->
				<div class="absolute -top-24 right-0 -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl" aria-hidden="true">
					<div class="aspect-[1404/767] w-[87.75rem] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff4694] to-[#776fff] opacity-25" style="clip-path: polygon(73.6% 51.7%, 91.7% 11.8%, 100% 46.4%, 97.4% 82.2%, 92.5% 84.9%, 75.7% 64%, 55.3% 47.5%, 46.5% 49.4%, 45% 62.9%, 50.3% 87.2%, 21.3% 64.1%, 0.1% 100%, 5.4% 51.1%, 21.4% 63.9%, 58.9% 0.2%, 73.6% 51.7%)"></div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Featured Section -->
			<section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
				<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
					<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center mb-16">
						<h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Philosophy</h2>
						<p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">왜 바이브 코딩인가?</p>
						<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
							단순히 로직을 구현하는 것을 넘어, 도구와 하나가 되어 흐름을 타는 즐거움을 추구합니다.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
						<dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
							<div class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:border-purple-100 group">
								<dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-slate-900">
									<div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-600 text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
										🚀
									</div>
									High Performance
								</dt>
								<dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
									<p class="flex-auto italic font-light">"Astro의 정적 사이트 생성을 통해 사용자에게 가장 빠른 경험을 선사합니다."</p>
								</dd>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:border-purple-100 group">
								<dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-slate-900">
									<div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-600 text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
										🤖
									</div>
									AI Collaboration
								</dt>
								<dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
									<p class="flex-auto italic font-light">"AI 비서와 협업하며 생산성을 극대화하는 실전 노하우를 공유합니다."</p>
								</dd>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:border-purple-100 group">
								<dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-slate-900">
									<div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-600 text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
										✨
									</div>
									Modern Stack
								</dt>
								<dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
									<p class="flex-auto italic font-light">"Tailwind CSS와 최신 라이브러리를 활용한 감각적인 UI를 구현합니다."</p>
								</dd>
							</div>
						</dl>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
